ëíŸ@cee3c04c8a663de7c460936cec34d5e71f5988b433f5dd02d4be16657d42a6a1⁄Title: This week in Nu #4
Path: This week in Nu #4
Content:
A few new commands and more polish this week and a surprise contribution of sublime-style fuzzy history searching.
Added a new 
``env``
 command to display environment variables and important paths (
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/675] #675
)
pka added a sublime-style fuzzy history search (
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/672] #672
)
pka also added support for displaying the history and config paths to 
``env``
 (
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/690] #690
, 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/691] #691
)
Replaced the 
``vtable``
 command with the new 
``pivot``
 command (
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/678] #678
)
Added support for urlencode/urldecode (
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/685] #685
)
wycats moved more internals to use metadata tags (
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/668] #668
)
Thanks to those who filed issues: tlightsky, larsch, and jankoprowski
Lots of bugfixes
